### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 1. Employee → Get Own Timesheets (SHOULD WORK)
### ------------------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:4004/me
Authorization: Basic jatin:

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 2. Employee → Try Manager API (SHOULD FAIL ❌)
### ------------------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:4004/mana
x-user: emp1
x-roles: Employee

### Employee → Get Own Timesheets
GET http://localhost:4004/employee/MyTimesheets
Authorization: Basic jatin:

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 3. Manager → Get Pending Approvals (SHOULD WORK)
### ------------------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:4004/manager/PendingApprovals
x-user: mgr1
x-roles: Manager


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 4. Manager → Approve Timesheet (SHOULD WORK)
### ------------------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:4004/manager/approveTimesheet
Content-Type: application/json
x-user: mgr1
x-roles: Manager

{
  "timesheetId": "TS001",
  "remarks": "Approved"
}


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 5. Employee → Try Approve (SHOULD FAIL ❌)
### ------------------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:4004/manager/approveTimesheet
Content-Type: application/json
x-user: emp1
x-roles: Employee

{
  "timesheetId": "TS001",
  "remarks": "Trying unauthorized"
}


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 6. Employee → Submit Timesheet (SHOULD WORK)
### ------------------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:4004/employee/submitTimesheet
Content-Type: application/json
x-user: emp1
x-roles: Employee

{
  "timesheetId": "TS001"
}


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 7. No Role → Should FAIL ❌
### ------------------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:4004/employee/MyTimesheets
x-user: randomUser


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 8. Debug → Check current user
### ------------------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:4004/employee/whoAmI
x-user: emp1
x-roles: Employee